text: Louise Parker (born 10 December 1942) is a Canadian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Canada Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Montreal Category:Pan American Games medalists in gymnastics Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Canada Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Canada Category:Gymnasts at the 1959 Pan American Games
